metadata.description:
fx_doughs is a generative project based on our original "DONUT HEADS" design created by @dirtyblackghost(Twitter) and first used in 2017. The signature design was made for the Butternut Deluxe podcast promotional and social media posts. Since entering the NFT space in 2021 (February) and watching the rise of PFP/collectable projects we always wanted to make our own. With fx_hash and @PureSpider(Twitter) template we realized this dream of making a project like this. Enjoy!

